=== Etymology ===
From Latin ''[[sub]]'' meaning "below" or "under", and ''[[fixus]]'', perfect passive participle of ''[[figere]]'' meaning "fasten".

== [[Noun]] ==
#one or more letters or sounds added at the end of a word to modify the word's meaning
#: Example: word ''sing'' + suffix ''able'', result ''singable''

